# Build outputs
**/bin
**/obj
**/out
**/publish
**/*.suo
**/*.user

# Git / VCS
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.gitattributes

# Editors / IDEs
**/.vs
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/.history

# Docker — never copy the Dockerfile itself or local compose overrides into
# the build context.
**/Dockerfile
**/.dockerignore
**/docker-compose*.yml
**/docker-compose*.yaml

# Tooling caches
**/.tool-cache
**/.local
**/.config

# OS junk
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/Desktop.ini

# Misc
**/*.log
**/*.tmp
**/*.bak
**/README.md
